<form action="/pilot" method="post">
  <div>
    <label for="pilot[user_id]">Eve User ID:</label> <input name="pilot[user_id]" type="text" value="<%= @pilot.user_id %>"/>
  </div>
  <div>
    <label for="pilot[api_key]">Eve API Key:</label> <input name="pilot[api_key]" type="text" value="<%= @pilot.api_key %>"/>
  </div>
  <div>
    <label for="pilot[email]">Email:</label> <input name="pilot[email]" type="text" value="<%= @pilot.email %>"/><br/>
    <span style="color: grey; font-size: small">If left blank, will use your google email address.</span>
  </div>
  <div>
    <label for="pilot[monitor]">Send empty queue warnings?</label> <input name="pilot[monitor]" type="checkbox" value="1" <%= 'checked="checked"' if @pilot.monitor %>/>
  </div>
  <input type="submit" value="update"/>
</form>

Numeric User ID, and API Key can be found at <a href="http://www.eveonline.com/api/default.asp" target="_new">EVE API Key Management</a> page.

